title: Boulder (disambiguation)
content:
This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.

Boulder may refer to:

  • NPCs:
    • Boulder - a Weiss troll
  • Agility obstacles and shortcuts:
    • Boulder (dense essence mine)
    • Boulder (God Wars Dungeon)
  • The main minable rock in the Volcanic Mine:
    • Giant Boulder (attached)
    • Giant Boulder (unattached)
    • Large Boulder
    • Medium Boulder
    • Small Boulder
  • Other:
    • Boulder (Viyeldi caves) - the boulders encountered in the Viyeldi caves during the Legends' Quest
    • Giant boulder - a reward from the 2020 Christmas event
    • Boulder - scenery used to set deadfall traps
    • Sandy boulder - a hidden king sand crab
